---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const whatsappUrl = 'https://wa.me/60175032281?text=Hi%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20marketing%20for%20my%20law%20firm.';

const practiceAreas = [
  { name: 'Divorce & Family Law', slug: 'divorce-lawyer', desc: 'Clients in distress, searching privately. Empathy-first marketing.' },
  { name: 'Criminal Defence', slug: 'criminal-defence', desc: 'High urgency, high emotion. Every hour matters.' },
  { name: 'Personal Injury', slug: 'personal-injury', desc: "They're searching from a hospital bed. Meet them there." },
  { name: 'Corporate Law', slug: 'corporate-law', desc: 'Longer sales cycle, higher value. Reputation is everything.' },
  { name: 'Property & Conveyancing', slug: 'property-conveyancing', desc: 'Transactional, competitive, local. Win on trust and speed.' },
  { name: 'Immigration', slug: 'immigration-lawyer', desc: 'Complex journeys, anxious clients. Clarity converts.' },
  { name: 'Employment Law', slug: 'employment-lawyer', desc: 'Employees and employers both searching — different funnels.' },
  { name: 'Estate Planning', slug: 'estate-planning', desc: "Nobody wants to think about this. Make it feel manageable." },
];

import { AISearchDemo } from '../components/react/AISearchDemo';
import { WhatWeDo } from '../components/react/WhatWeDo';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Lawyer Marketing Malaysia — The Bar Council Just Changed the Rules"
  description="Malaysian lawyers can now advertise. Most firms haven't moved yet. We help law firms build their client pipeline before the competition catches up."
>

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section class="bg-cream py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <span class="section-label">For Malaysian Law Firms</span>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-teal-deep mb-6 leading-tight">
        For the first time, Malaysian lawyers can advertise.
        <span class="text-copper">Most firms are still waiting.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-charcoal/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-body">
        The Bar Council's rule change created a window. The firms that build their online presence
        now will own their practice area — before the market gets crowded.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-primary">See How It Works</a>
        <a href="/en/niches/" class="btn-secondary">Find Your Practice Area</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== THE SHIFT ===== -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <span class="section-label">The Shift</span>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-teal-deep mb-6">
        Something just changed in Malaysian law.
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-charcoal/75 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          For decades, the Bar Council prohibited lawyers from advertising. Word of mouth,
          referrals, personal reputation — that was all you had. And if you were good, that was enough.
        </p>
        <p>
          But the rules have changed. Advertising is now permitted. And while most firms are still
          debating whether it's "appropriate," a small number are already building their digital
          presence — claiming the Google searches, the content authority, the online reputation —
          in every practice area across Malaysia.
        </p>
        <p>
          Here's what matters: <strong class="text-teal-deep">in digital marketing, the early mover
          advantage is structural.</strong> The firm that ranks first for "divorce lawyer Kuala Lumpur"
          today won't easily be displaced tomorrow. SEO compounds. Reputation compounds. Waiting doesn't.
        </p>
        <p>
          That's why we exist. Not to turn lawyers into billboards. But to help serious firms build
          something dignified, effective, and permanent — before the market gets noisy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== AI SEARCH DEMO ===== -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-cream-dark/50 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="section-label">AI Advantage</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-teal-deep mb-4">
          Get <span class="text-copper">AI-Cited</span> on Page 1
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          When potential clients ask AI for legal help, it recommends firms with the strongest digital presence. 
          We position you as the trusted choice.
        </p>
      </div>
      <AISearchDemo client:visible />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== PRACTICE AREAS ===== -->
  <section class="bg-cream-dark py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="section-label">Practice Areas</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-teal-deep mb-4">
          We don't do "general" legal marketing.<br class="hidden sm:block"> Neither should you.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A person searching for a criminal defence lawyer at 2am is nothing like a business owner
          looking for corporate counsel over lunch. We build strategies around how <em>your</em>
          specific clients think, search, and decide.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        {practiceAreas.map(area => (
          <a href={`/en/niches/${area.slug}/`}
             class="group bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-cream-dark hover:border-teal/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-teal-deep group-hover:text-teal transition mb-2">
              {area.name}
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/55 leading-relaxed mb-3">{area.desc}</p>
            <span class="text-copper text-sm font-semibold">See the strategy &rarr;</span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/en/niches/" class="text-teal-deep font-semibold hover:text-copper transition text-sm">
          View all 20 practice areas &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== WHAT WE DO ===== -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="section-label">Our Deliverables</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-teal-deep mb-4">
          A Complete Digital <span class="text-copper">Ecosystem</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We don't just "run ads." We build a permanent, professional infrastructure that positions you as the authority in your practice area.
        </p>
      </div>

      <WhatWeDo client:visible />
    </div>
  </section>

      <!-- Services row -->
      <div class="mt-12 bg-teal-deep rounded-xl p-8 sm:p-10 text-white">
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm text-copper mb-2">SEO & Local SEO</h4>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Rank for the searches your clients actually make. Google Business Profile, location pages, content strategy.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm text-copper mb-2">Google Ads (SEM)</h4>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Immediate leads from high-intent searchers while your SEO builds momentum.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm text-copper mb-2">GEO</h4>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Generative Engine Optimisation — be the firm AI recommends when clients ask ChatGPT for a lawyer.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm text-copper mb-2">Landing Pages</h4>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              A complete, professional landing page for your firm from <strong class="text-copper">RM300/year</strong>. No hidden fees.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== THE STAKES ===== -->
  <section class="bg-teal-deep text-white py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <span class="section-label !text-copper">Why Now</span>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        The firms that move first will be the hardest to displace.
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-white/65 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-left sm:text-center">
        <p>
          Think about how you choose a restaurant in a new city. You Google it. You look at the
          first few results. You read the reviews. You pick one.
        </p>
        <p>
          Your future clients do exactly the same thing when they need a lawyer. The only question
          is whether they find you — or the firm down the road that started six months earlier.
        </p>
        <p>
          SEO isn't a switch you flip. It's a garden you plant. The firms planting now will be the
          ones clients find next year, and the year after that. The ones who wait will spend twice
          as much to catch up — <strong class="text-white">if they can catch up at all.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== FINAL CTA ===== -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-teal-deep mb-4">
        You've spent years building your reputation in the courtroom.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-charcoal/60 mb-3">
        Let's make sure the right clients can find you.
      </p>
      <p class="text-charcoal/45 text-sm mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
        We'll review your practice area, show you where the opportunities are, and give you
        an honest assessment — even if the answer is "you don't need us."
      </p>
      <a href={whatsappUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-copper text-base px-10 py-4">
        Get a Free Practice Area Review
      </a>
      <p class="text-xs text-charcoal/35 mt-4">No obligation. No hard sell. Just clarity.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
